      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FEDERAL BLAST (1) goes very well over this track and trip including three wins. Comes off a (21.87) win last time, scoring by 4 lengths in a Grade 5 over 380m at this track. Rates on top and should go close. SMOOTH BLAST (8) has been in super consistent form, finishing in the minors at his last four runs. Last start finished 3rd in a Grade 5/6 on March 31 over 498m at this track behind She's Spirited beaten 2.5 lengths (29.02). Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Hard to beat again. SHINE ON SKI (2) turned spotting a big start finishing eighth (23.74) last time in a Grade 4 at this track. Comes through a solid form race last start. Expected to give a good account. HIGH GEAR MARIA (7) is always a threat when she races at this track and distance.",
